Text: Countries with access to Clickpaper Cc Dear Mark and Tana After reviewing the password applications available on the Clickpaper and EnronOnline websites it appears that several countries have access to EOL but not to Clickpaper please see attached Since due dilligence has already been completed for the EOL countries and soon Clickpaper will migrate to the EnronOnline trading platform it seems it might not be too difficult to add mirroring Clickpaper password applications Is that the case We have business interests in several of the countries accessible solely via EOL Best regards Marla Thompson Clickpapercom Marketing

The Weekly Clickpaper Activity Report is BackThe following report shows which Registered Guest and Internal Users logged onto Clickpaper and how many days they logged on between Monday October nd and Friday October th Please keep in mind that some of the Guest User logons are from me logging on with their IDs to preset filters or testing their IDs to ensure they are functional before I call them to encourage them to become Registered Users Please let me know if you have any questions This report will be issued weekly Best regards Marla Thompson Enron Forest Products Clickpaper Marketing
